Review Text: Worst service I had ever seen that I lost my money,bloody idiots don't know the value of money and food,have some values and dedication towards customers.

I have ordered looking at the rating, it was almost 11:15pm so that the order delivers before the time. 11:45pm i haved called the Zomato valet to enquire about the order status he said that he will reach the cakesclub in 2 mins to pick the order and said he will reach the place on time.
I again called the valet at 11:55pm looking the order status is still being prepared and valet informed me that the resturant is not yet prepared the cake. The cakes are always preserved well in advance, so why does the restaurant took so much time to handover the cake.
At around 12:10am the order is delivered and went inside. I opened the packing with great excitement and finally looking at the cake situation i was shocked and disappointed, it is like the face of Oberyn Martell crushed by Mountain in GOT only the hardcore fans can understand it.
I said okay inside and asked my brother to cut the cake but the taste of cake is not at all okay and it is melted and moved from the cake base.
Very much disappointed , think twice before placing the order.
